<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ABU Lernportal – Detail</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --t1:#C0392B; --t2:#E67E22; --t3:#27AE60;
    --t4:#2980B9; --t5:#F39C12; --t6:#8E44AD; --t7:#6C3483; --t8:#1a5276; --t9:#145a32; --t10:#117a65;
    --g9:#111827; --g7:#374151; --g5:#6B7280; --g3:#D1D5DB; --g1:#F3F4F6;
  }
  * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  body { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; background:#F0F2F5; color:var(--g7); }

  .wrap { max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; padding:2rem 1.5rem 5rem; }

  .back-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:var(--g5); text-decoration:none; margin-bottom:1.75rem; transition:color .15s; }
  .back-btn:hover { color:var(--g9); }

  .d-header { border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:1.75rem; display:grid; grid-template-columns:5px 1fr; box-shadow:0 3px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .d-stripe { }
  .d-head-body { padding:22px 24px; display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:16px; }
  .d-big-num { font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif; font-size:64px; font-weight:800; line-height:1; opacity:0.18; flex-shrink:0; min-width:60px; }
  .d-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:3px; }
  .d-title { font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:800; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--g9); letter-spacing:-0.3px; line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .d-desc { font-size:12px; color:var(--g5); line-height:1.5; }

  .file-cards { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }

  .file-card { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:16px 18px; background:white; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition:all .18s; border:1.5px solid transparent; }
  .file-card:hover { border-color:var(--tc,#333); transform:translateX(4px); box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.09); }

  .file-icon { width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:10px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:18px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .fi-t { background:#DBEAFE; } .fi-e { background:#DCFCE7; } .fi-q { background:#FCE7F3; }

  .file-body { flex:1; }
  .file-name { font-weight:600; font-size:14px; color:var(--g9); margin-bottom:2px; }
  .file-hint { font-size:11px; color:var(--g5); }

  .file-arrow { font-size:16px; color:var(--g3); transition:all .15s; }
  .file-card:hover .file-arrow { color:var(--tc,#333); transform:translateX(3px); }

  .not-linked { opacity:0.5; cursor:default; }
  .not-linked:hover { transform:none; box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); border-color:transparent; }

  .info-box { background:#FFF3CD; border:1px solid #F0C040; border-radius:10px; padding:12px 16px; font-size:12px; color:#856404; margin-top:1rem; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <a class="back-btn" href="#" onclick="event.preventDefault(); history.back();">← Zurück zur Übersicht</a>

  <div class="d-header" id="dHeader">
    <div class="d-stripe" id="dStripe"></div>
    <div class="d-head-body" id="dHeadBody">
      <div class="d-big-num" id="dNum"></div>
      <div>
        <div class="d-label" id="dLabel"></div>
        <div class="d-title" id="dTitle"></div>
        <div class="d-desc" id="dDesc"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="file-cards" id="fileCards"></div>
  <div class="info-box">💡 Klicke auf eine Karte um die Datei zu öffnen. Falls noch kein Link hinterlegt ist, wende dich an deine Lehrperson.</div>
</div>

